Condor arrived to Maximal Base and looking to Rodimus, said "Where's 
the Commander Talon... ? I want to report that I'm back from my 
patrol" 


At the same time, Nightlight arrived to base and she pointing at 
Rodimus said to Vampirtron "Vampirtron, he's our commander Rodimus 
Prime... " 


"Commander???" replied Condor "What did happen with Talon?"
